Sir Rod Stewart, 77, was snapped at the house of The Kardashians star Scott Disick with his daughter Kimberly, 42.In clips shared to Scott’s Instagram Story, Rod could be seen helping Kimberly organise her long-time friend’s pantry.Kourtney Kardashian’s ex could be heard saying: “That is some pantry Kim that you have made...get to work!“At least it’s Rodrick approved.”Kimberly started her organising company, The Realm, last year and transforms the homes of her celebrity friends.